name: .QMAP File Extension
summary: Learn about .QMAP files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: A QMAP file contains level data for QWERUIOP, a rhythm game developed by Game IQ. It is a Zip-compressed archive that stores playable level information, such as the beats per minute and length. QWERUIOP gamers can export and import QMAP files to share levels with other gamers.

content: QWERUIOP is a rhythm game that involves pressing the QWERUIOP keys on a keyboard at the correct times to music. Players can import .MP3 music files into the Windows version of QWERUIOP or upload them to the web version to make them playable.

instructions: You can open a QMAP file with QWERUIOP in Windows or a web browser. To open a QMAP file with the Windows version of QWERUIOP, select Import Level.
